name: Squirmer Dream Eater
description:
This Squirmer is called Dream Eater. 

Squirmers are forever-moving worm-like cylinders. All that they do is squirming around and nothing else. They don't eat or die. They don’t have a purpose in life. Whatever they do, it won't make much difference. 

This is an animated 3D model. There is a potential to place it in the Metaverse/virtual world where you live in.
